reviewText:
Great set of superior movies, starting with From Wings Came Flight: a forever classic of modern Skydiving!
Perfection of the Skydiving cinematography and its golden standard worldwide.
The video and sound quality are VHS quality. The sound is just Stereo. Doesn't have a narrator for the video secuence.
This product was exactly what it claimed to be.  Gave it to my son who is a skydiver and he loves it.
